# Fix CI Errors

When invoked, follow the `snacky_fix-ci` skill at `.cursor/skills/snacky_fix-ci/SKILL.md`.

## Quick Reference

1. **Fetch failures**: `gh run list --limit 5` then `gh run view <RUN_ID> --log-failed`
2. **Classify**: Lint, TypeCheck, Test, Security, Build, or Migration error
3. **Fix**: Edit the source files to resolve each error
4. **Verify locally**: Run `pnpm lint`, `pnpm typecheck`, `pnpm test` before pushing
5. **Push & watch**: Commit, push, then `gh run watch`

Always read the full error log before fixing — never guess. If all checks pass, report success and stop.
